        FIRST_I_REGRET_TO_SAY_THAT_WHILE_WE                                   = 11063,  -- First, I regret to say that while we continued our search for clues surrounding the fiery object in your absence, we found nothing of import.
        WE_WOULD_HAVE_YOU_RETURN_TO_EAST_RONFAURE                             = 11064,  -- We would have you return to East Ronfaure and locate any object that may shed light on the mystery before us.
        ONCE_YOU_HAVE_FOUND_THREE_BRING_THEM_BACK                             = 11065,  -- Once you have found three, bring them back here for inspection.
        THAT_IS_UNFORTUNATE_HOWEVER_I_SHALL_BE_WAITING                        = 11066,  -- That is unfortunate. However, I shall be waiting here if you happen to have a change of heart.
        WELCOME_BACK_WERE_YOU_SUCCESSFUL_IN_YOUR_INVESTIGATION                = 11067,  -- Welcome back, %. Were you successful in your investigation?
        WHY_THIS_LOOKS_LIKE_THE_BLADE_OF_A                                    = 11068,  -- Why, this looks like the blade of a windmill... But the closest ones lie hundreds of malms away in the Konschtat Highlands...
        AND_THESE_CRYSTALS_THE_FORMATIONS_SEEM_TO_HAVE                        = 11069,  -- And these crystals... The formations seem to have continued growing even after they pierced the wood...
        FINALLY_THIS_PLATE_I_BELIEVE_I_CAN_MAKE                               = 11070,  -- Finally, this plate... I believe I can make out the letters E, O, and...S...
        EOS_WHAT_ON_VANA_DIEL_COULD_IT_MEAN                                   = 11071,  -- Eos? What on Vana'diel could it mean...?
        I_SEE_ONE_OF_YOUR_RECRUITS_HAS_COME                                   = 11072,  -- I see one of your recruits has come across some items of ours. If you would be so kind as to hand them over immediately.
        STAND_DOWN_KNAVE_STATE_YOUR_NAME_AND_WHENCE                           = 11073,  -- Stand down, knave! State your name and whence you came!
        AH_AND_THIS_WOULD_BE_A_PORTION_OF                                     = 11074,  -- Ah, and this would be a portion of the right propeller. I clearly expressed my doubts about the pliability of elm...
        DO_NOT_MAKE_ME_REPEAT_MYSELF                                          = 11075,  -- Do not make me repeat myself!
        OUR_FEARS_AS_TO_THE_FATE_OF_THE                                       = 11076,  -- Our fears as to the fate of the Eos are confir--
        SPENCER                                                               = 11077,  -- Spencer!
        I_APOLOGIZE_FOR_MY_COLLEAGUE_S_LACK_OF                                = 11078,  -- I apologize for my colleague's lack of refinement. The items you have recovered are the lawful property of the archduke of Jeuno and must be transported back to the Duchy for further study.
        ABSURD_YOUR_LAWS_HAVE_NO_AUTHORITY_HERE_IN                            = 11079,  -- Absurd! Your laws have no authority here in San d'Oria!
        NOW_BEGONE_AT_ONCE_BEFORE_I_AM_INCLINED                               = 11080,  -- Now begone at once before I am inclined to use force!
        CAPTAIN_YOU_WILL_ABIDE_BY_THE_WISHES_OF                               = 11081,  -- Captain. You will abide by the wishes of our venerable guests from Jeuno.
        COMMANDER_BUT_I                                                       = 11082,  -- Commander! But I--
        THAT_IS_ENOUGH_SIR_MAINCHELITE_WHAT_IS_YOUR                           = 11083,  -- That is enough, Sir Mainchelite. What is your duty as Royal Knight captain?
        SIR_TO_PROTECT_THE_KING_AND_ENFORCE_HIS                               = 11084,  -- Sir! To protect the king and enforce his will. But I do not see h--
        HIS_MAJESTY_HAS_GRANTED_THE_DUCAL_AMBASSADORS_FULL                    = 11085,  -- His Majesty has granted the ducal ambassadors full authority regarding this investigation. Impertinence will not be tolerated.
        HMPH_AN_OUTRAGE_WITH_WHAT_MANNER_OF_SOPHISTRIES                       = 11086,  -- Hmph! An outrage! With what manner of sophistries have these fiends poisoned our king?
        I_WILL_IGNORE_THAT_OUTBURST_SIR_KNIGHT_NOW                            = 11087,  -- I will ignore that outburst, Sir Knight. Now, I believe you heard the commander. Hand over the items.
        MAINCHELITE_RELUCTANTLY_HANDS_GERWULF_THE_THE_AND_THE                 = 11088,  -- Mainchelite reluctantly hands Gerwulf the %, the %, and the %.
        ON_BEHALF_OF_THE_ARCHDUKE_I_THANK_THE                                 = 11089,  -- On behalf of the archduke, I thank the Royal Knights for their assistance in this matter. And as a precaution, we ask that you do not speak of your findings to anyone, understood?
        THE_INCORPORATION_OF_ADDITIONAL_CONTROL_FLAPS_IN_CONJUNCTION          = 11090,  -- ...the incorporation of additional control flaps in conjunction with an upgrade from elm to mahoga--
        SPENCER_LET_US_BE_ON_OUR_WAY                                          = 11091,  -- Spencer! Let us be on our way.
        HOLD_OUTSIDERS                                                        = 11092,  -- Hold, outsiders.
        MIGHT_YOU_BE_SPEAKING_TO_US_COMMANDER                                 = 11093,  -- Might you be speaking to us, Commander?
        YOU_HAVE_WORN_DRY_YOUR_WELCOME_TRAVELERS_DO                           = 11094,  -- You have worn dry your welcome, travelers. Do not expect a reprise of the king's generosity, should another misfortune befall your nation.
        I_SHALL_RELAY_THAT_TO_THE_ARCHDUKE_SIR                                = 11095,  -- ...... I shall relay that to the archduke, sir. Good day.
        AH_A_NEW_RECRUIT_PERHAPS                                              = 11096,  -- Ah, a new recruit, perhaps?
        I_APOLOGIZE_FOR_THE_DISPLAY_HOWEVER_IT_MAY                            = 11097,  -- I apologize for the display. However it may pain us, our first and foremost duty is to uphold the will of the king.
        REMEMBER_THAT_IF_THERE_IS_ANYTHING_ELSE_YOU                           = 11098,  -- Remember that. If there is anything else you require, speak with Lady Fiaudie yonder. She will brief you on your new responsibilities.
        I_COMMEND_YOU_ON_YOUR_PERFORMANCE_YOU_HAVE                            = 11099,  -- I commend you on your performance, %. You have displayed great courage and ingenuity, and proved your worth thricefold. You are hereby granted admission to the Knights of the Iron Ram. Congratulations.
        PLEASE_ACCEPT_THIS_TO_COMMEND_THE_BEGINNING_OF                        = 11100,  -- Please accept this % to commend the beginning of your military career. Speak with Evaluation Official Fiaudie for a detailed briefing on the decoration.
        YOU_ARE_NOW_A_MEMBER_OF_THE_KNIGHTS                                   = 11101,  -- You are now a member of the Knights of the Iron Ram!
        YOU_WISH_TO_REJOIN_THE_RANKS_OF_THE                                   = 11102,  -- You wish to rejoin the ranks of the Iron Rams? Splendid! Speak with Sir Houilloumie to begin your reinstatement.
        HOWDY_PARDNER_Y_KNOW_WHADDA_LADYBUG_IS_BEETLE                         = 11103,  -- Howdy, pardner! Y'know whadda ladybug is? Beetle-like vermin, red shell with black spots... Ring a cowbell?
        AHHH_SORRY_SORRY_THE_NAME_S_WYATT_AN                                  = 11104,  -- Ahhh, sorry, sorry. The name's Wyatt, an' I be an armor merchant from Jeuno. Ended up 'ere in San d'Oria some way or another, though.
        T_TELL_YOU_THE_TRUTH_JES_BETWEEN_YOU                                  = 11105,  -- T'tell you the truth, jes' between you an' me, a friend o' mine in the industry let me in on a little rumor's bayn goin' around. Seems there's a new type o' armor's bayn developed as o' late.
        AN_APPARENTLY_IT_TAKES_A_RAHT_MESS_O                                  = 11106,  -- An' apparently, it takes a raht mess o' % t'make it.
        SEEIN_AS_HOW_I_BE_JES_A_LOWLY                                         = 11107,  -- Seein' as how I be jes' a lowly merchant, I can't jes' go out an' start killin' ladybugs whenever I fancy. So I'm lookin' t'buy up as many as I can, an' then t'make a fortu--I mean, to aid in the war effort. Y'know, do mah part. Dewty as a citizen an' all that.
        THAT_S_WHERE_YOU_COME_IN_I_WAS                                        = 11108,  -- That's where you come in. I was thinkin' t'mahself, an experienced adventurer such as yurself maht be able t'help me out.
        IF_YOU_COULD_GET_YUR_HANDS_ON_SOME                                    = 11109,  -- If you could get yur hands on some % and sell 'em to me four adda time, I'd be willin' t'pay a pretty gil fur 'em.
        Y_GET_SOME_GIL_IN_YUR_POCKET_I                                        = 11110,  -- Y'get some gil in yur pocket, I get the materials I need. Sounds like a win-win situation t'me.
        NO_NEED_T_RUSH_JES_BRING_ME_SOME                                      = 11111,  -- No need t'rush. Jes' bring me some % whenever you gedda chance.
        WOULDN_T_HAPPEN_TO_HAVE_COME_ACROSS_ANY                               = 11112,  -- Wouldn't happen to have come across any more o' them %, would you? If you do, make sure you bring 'em t'me. Mah offer's still good.
        OOOH_NOW_THESE_LL_DO_JES_FINE_PERFECT                                 = 11113,  -- Oooh! Now these'll do jes' fine! Perfect shape, an' look at that shine! A splendid bunch o' % indeed!
        ALL_RIGHT_YOU_KEPT_YUR_SIDE_O_THE                                     = 11114,  -- All right, you kept yur side o' the bargain, so I'll do the same. Hope you don't mind Jeuno coinage.
        HEY_WOULD_THAT_BE_YOU_GOT_THERE                                       = 11115,  -- Hey, would that be % you got there?
        Y_SEE_I_HAPPEN_T_BE_A_PLAYER                                          = 11116,  -- Y'see, I happen t'be a player on the stock market. So if you're in a bind as t'what to do with that, I'd be willin' t'trade you cash fur it.
        Y_WANT_GIL_YOU_SAY_YOU_ONE_O                                          = 11117,  -- Y'want gil, you say? You one o' them cosmopolitan types?
        LESSEE_NOW_TAKIN_THE_CURRENT_MARKET_SITUATION_INTO                    = 11118,  -- Lessee now... Takin' the current market situation into account, this'll cash in fur around # gil. Alrighty then, here's yur gil. Minus commission, that is.
        THE_KING_S_FOREST_IS_CRAWLING_WITH_ORCS                               = 11119,  -- The king's forest is crawling with Orcs! Take care, lest you find yourself roasting on a spit over one of their campfires!
        OR_WOULD_YOU_RATHER_STAY_WITHIN_THE_CITY                              = 11120,  -- Or would you rather stay within the city walls?
        BRAVE_THE_WILDS_YES_NO                                                = 11121,  -- Brave the wilds? Yes. No.
        THE_MINSTREL_OF_MELODIES_IS_MY_NAME_FOR                               = 11122,  -- The minstrel of melodies is my name, For a mere # gil I'll recall your past. Your stories of love, anger, triumph, and shame, The river of memories runs deep and vast.
        THE_MINSTREL_OF_MELODIES_IS_MY_NAME_FOR_2                             = 11123,  -- The minstrel of melodies is my name, For a mere # gil I'd recall your past. But I find that you're lacking in cash or in fame, So until that time, my kind offer will last.
        NOW_CLOSE_YOUR_EYES                                                   = 11124,  -- Now close your eyes...
        WHICH_MEMORY_WILL_YOU_HAVE_RECALLED_NOTHING_WINGS                     = 11125,  -- Which memory will you have recalled? Nothing. Wings of the Goddess Missions. San d'Oria Quests 1. San d'Oria Quests 2. San d'Oria Quests 3. Other Quests. Rhapsodies of Vana'diel.
