        WHICH_MEMORY_WILL_YOU_HAVE_RECALLED_NOTHING_STEAMED                   = 11127,  -- Which memory will you have recalled? Nothing. Steamed Rams(pt.1). Steamed Rams(pt.2). Steamed Rams(pt.3). Steamed Rams(pt.4). Steamed Rams(pt.5). Gifts of the Griffon(pt.1). Gifts of the Griffon(pt.2). Gifts of the Griffon(pt.3). Gifts of the Griffon(pt.4). Gifts of the Griffon(pt.5). Gifts of the Griffon(pt.6). Claws of the Griffon. Boy and the Beast(pt.1). Boy and the Beast(pt.2). Wrath of the Griffon(pt.1). Wrath of the Griffon(pt.2). Beans Ahoy!(pt.1). Beans Ahoy!(pt.2). Beans Ahoy!(pt.3). Beans Ahoy!(pt.4).
        WHICH_MEMORY_WILL_YOU_HAVE_RECALLED_NOTHING_PERILS                    = 11128,  -- Which memory will you have recalled? Nothing. Perils of the Griffon(pt.1). Perils of the Griffon(pt.2). Perils of the Griffon(pt.3). Perils of the Griffon(pt.4). Perils of the Griffon(pt.5). In a Haze of Glory(pt.1). In a Haze of Glory(pt.2). The Price of Valor(pt.1). The Price of Valor(pt.2). Bonds That Never Die(pt.1). Bonds That Never Die(pt.2). Songbirds in a Snowstorm(pt.1). Songbirds in a Snowstorm(pt.2). Son and Father(pt.1). Son and Father(pt.2). Son and Father(pt.3). Son and Father(pt.4). Chasing Shadows.
        WHICH_MEMORY_WILL_YOU_HAVE_RECALLED_NOTHING_BEAST                     = 11129,  -- Which memory will you have recalled? Nothing. Beast from the East(pt.1). Beast from the East(pt.2). Beast from the East(pt.3). Beast from the East(pt.4). Beast from the East(pt.5). Beast from the East(pt.6). Beast from the East(pt.7). Beast from the East(pt.8). Beast from the East(pt.9).
