        THERE_ARE_SO_MANY_CHOICES_RESOURCE_PROCUREMENT_MILITARY               = 11200,  -- There are so many choices... Resource procurement. Military supply procurement. Logistics. Stronghold outfitting. Weapons production. Weapons development. Public security. Stronghold fortification. I require more time to consider.
