        THIS_OPERATION_REQUIRES_THAT_YOU_INFILTRATE_AN_AREA                   = 11613,  -- This operation requires that you infiltrate an area under beastman control and launch an attack on one of their strongholds, allowing our main forces to gain influence in the region.
