        THE_ADORABLE_LITTLE_TARUTARU_WITH_THE_BLONDE_BRAIDS                   = 11740,  -- The adorable little Tarutaru with the blonde braids is laying plaster. Gonna have to get her on some ice crystals.
        THE_HUME_LADY_IS_A_STONEMASON_AND_A                                   = 11741,  -- The Hume lady is a stonemason, and a darn good one. She's gonna be needin' wind crystals.
        THAT_OLD_COOT_OF_AN_ELVAAN_WITH_THE                                   = 11742,  -- That old coot of an Elvaan with the huge axe strapped across his back is a carpenter. Famous 'round these parts. Make sure you get him workin' with earth crystals.
        MAY_NOT_LOOK_IT_BUT_THE_MITHRA_WITH                                   = 11743,  -- May not look it, but the Mithra with the black kerchief wrapped 'round her noggin is an architect. She's gonna need her lightning crystals.
        THAT_SPRAT_OF_A_TARUTARU_WEARIN_THE_BLUE                              = 11744,  -- That sprat of a Tarutaru wearin' the blue getup's a handy lil' plumber. Surin' he'll be wantin' his water crystals, no doubt.
        THE_GOOD_LOOKING_FELLA_IN_ALL_WHITE_DOES                              = 11745,  -- The good-looking fella in all white does scaffoldin'. Young Hume lad. See to it he's usin' light crystals.
        THE_LADY_ELVAAN_S_A_PAINTER_HANDLES_A                                 = 11746,  -- The lady Elvaan's a painter. Handles a brush like nobody I never seen. Need dark crystals in that line of work. And that's it.
        AHHH_ONE_MORE_THING_IF_YOU_RE_TOO                                     = 11747,  -- Ahhh, one more thing. If you're too late issuin' your orders, they're liable to up and leave their posts. So be right, and be quick.
        CHOOSE_A_CRYSTAL_FIRE_CRYSTAL_ICE_CRYSTAL_WIND                        = 11748,  -- Choose a crystal! Fire crystal. Ice crystal. Wind crystal. Earth crystal. Lightning crystal. Water crystal. Light crystal. Dark crystal. Plumb give up.
        HEY_NOW_YOU_RE_RUNNIN_THIS_HERE_OPERATION                             = 11749,  -- Hey now, you're runnin' this here operation! You can't just quit! There's no quitting in war!
        WOW_YOU_SURE_BOTCHED_THAT_JOB_ALL_THEM                                = 11750,  -- Wow... You sure botched that job. All them wrong orders threw the craftsmen off kilter. They're demandin' a new foreman.
