        THE_POWER_OF_SONG_A_MYSTICAL_THING_THAT                               = 12090,  -- The power of song, a mystical thing That comes forth only when you sing. A minstrel's job in life is never done. So sing a doodle-doodle-lay And be upon your merry way-- And check your title, too, oh worthy one.t
        A_HERO_OF_OUR_TIME_THE_NAME_OF                                        = 12091,  -- %, a hero of our time! The name of % throughout the world will chimet
