        I_M_SURE_THEY_LL_BE_FINE_I                                            = 12660,  -- I'm sure they'll be fine. I mean, how could anyone rrresist the charms of two such handsome lads?
        THOSE_ROYAL_KNIGHTS_ARE_A_STUBBORN_LOT_ACCORDING                      = 12661,  -- Those Royal Knights are a stubborn lot according to the Tarutaru. I hear they put people to the sword for stepping out of line.
