        SO_YOU_RE_THE_NEW_SCOUT_EH_WELL                                       = 13033,  -- So you're the new scout, eh? Well, here then. Take this.
        YOU_DON_T_GET_TO_BE_A_SCOUT                                           = 13034,  -- You don't get to be a scout by just walking around carrying a bunch of stuff. You gotta be nimble! Now go drop some of that garbage and come back!
        ARE_YOU_FAMILIAR_WITH_FIENDTRAPPERS_FIEND_WHAT_NOW                    = 13035,  -- Are you familiar with fiendtrappers? Fiend what now? I practically invented them.
        HMPH_SOME_SCOUT_YOU_ARE_SIGH_THE_DEVICE                               = 13036,  -- Hmph...some scout you are. <Sigh>... The device I just issued you is called a fiendtrapper. Together with a blank fiend plate, it forms the latest in portable recording technology available to our army.
        CALM_DOWN_AND_LISTEN_NOW_WHEN_YOU_USE                                 = 13037,  -- Calm down and listen, now. When you use the fiendtrapper, the data will be recorded to the blank fiend plate inside. Quite a marvelous invention, really.
        GOT_IT_EVEN_YOU_MUST_HAVE_UNDERSTOOD_THAT                             = 13038,  -- Got it? Even you must have understood that explanation. Your orders are to take that device and gather enemy intel on those damnable Orcs!
        A_KNOW_IT_ALL_HUH_SUIT_YOURSELF_HOW                                   = 13039,  -- A know-it-all, huh? Suit yourself. How about going and getting your hands on some enemy surveillance, then?
        OFF_YOU_GO_NOW_THOSE_ORCS_AREN_T                                      = 13040,  -- Off you go, now. Those Orcs aren't going to...surveil themselves. Is that even a word?
        QUIT_WASTING_YOUR_TIME_I_DON_T_SEE                                    = 13041,  -- Quit wasting your time! I don't see any Orcs 'round here what needs spying on! Now get on with it!
        WHY_DO_YOU_INSIST_ON_BOTHERING_ME_GO                                  = 13042,  -- Why do you insist on bothering me? Go and report to Rasdinice immediately!
        WHAT_DO_YOU_WANT_SOME_OF_US_ARE                                       = 13043,  -- What do you want? Some of us are busy. Do you know what busy means? Or do you require an explanation for that, too?
        WELL_I_LL_BE_THIS_IS_ACTUALLY_A                                       = 13044,  -- Well, I'll be... This is actually a nice bit of work. I can even make out the type of grass they are using to make their mount straps! Not bad, scout. Now go and get some more.
        IS_THIS_SOME_KIND_OF_JOKE_I_CAN                                       = 13045,  -- Is this some kind of joke? I can't make out a single thing on this recording. Get your act together and find something material!
        DO_YOU_THINK_I_M_AS_BLIND_AS                                          = 13046,  -- Do you think I'm as blind as you are dull? The Orcs in this footage of yours are mere newborns, man! Now get back out there and find the real movers and shakers!
        WHO_ARE_YOU_TRYING_TO_FOOL_WEARING_ALL                                = 13047,  -- Who are you trying to fool wearing all those medals, huh? One would think with all that experience you'd at least have the common sense to spy on some veteran Orcs.
        YOU_VE_ALREADY_BROUGHT_IN_ENOUGH_INTEL_ON                             = 13048,  -- You've already brought in enough intel on that type of Orc. Rasdinice has instructed us to gather intel on as many different types as possible.
        NOT_HALF_BAD_SCOUT_EVERYTHING_S_IN_ORDER                              = 13049,  -- Not half bad, scout. Everything's in order here. See too it this information makes it's way to Rasdinice.
        THAT_S_GREAT_THAT_YOU_RE_ITCHING_TO                                   = 13050,  -- That's great that you're itching to get back out in the field. But first things first. Take the intel you have and report to Rasdinice.
        OH_HELLO_THERE_I_VE_HEARD_THAT_THERE                                  = 13051,  -- Oh, hello there! I've heard that there is some adventurer around here that has some ingenious ideas to help our troops in the struggle transport supplies. That wouldn't happen to be you now, would it?
        ALLOW_HIM_TO_RACK_YOUR_BRAIN_RACK_AWAY                                = 13052,  -- Allow him to rack your brain? Rack away. No racking this day.
        MY_MISTAKE_I_APOLOGIZE_FOR_TROUBLING_YOU                              = 13053,  -- My mistake. I apologize for troubling you.
        THANK_THE_GODDESS_I_VE_FOUND_YOU_AT                                   = 13054,  -- Thank the Goddess! I've found you at last! I'll give you all of the information I have concerning the conditions and terrain of our supply routes. Please, you must lend us your strategic brilliance!
        THE_MOST_RECENT_DATA_WE_HAVE_TELLS_US                                 = 13055,  -- The most recent data we have tells us the following.
        ACTUALLY_I_HAVE_NOTHING_OF_SIGNIFICANCE_TO_TELL                       = 13056,  -- Actually, I have nothing of significance to tell you. Our intel has brought in no new information.
        THE_LATEST_WEATHER_REPORT_INDICATES_THAT_THE_WEATHER                  = 13057,  -- The latest weather report indicates that the weather in [Xarcabard/Beaucedine Glacier/The Eldieme Necropolis/Crawlers' Nest/Garlaige Citadel/Batallia Downs/the Rolanberry Fields/Sauromugue Champaign/Jugner Forest/Pashhow Marshlands/the Meriphataud Mountains/Vunkerl Inlet/Grauberg/Fort Karugo-Narugo/East Ronfaure/North Gustaberg/West Sarutabaruta]will not hold up.
        THE_LATEST_WEATHER_REPORT_INDICATES_THAT_STORMS_CAN                   = 13058,  -- The latest weather report indicates that storms can be expected in [Xarcabard/Beaucedine Glacier/The Eldieme Necropolis/Crawlers' Nest/Garlaige Citadel/Batallia Downs/the Rolanberry Fields/Sauromugue Champaign/Jugner Forest/Pashhow Marshlands/the Meriphataud Mountains/Vunkerl Inlet/Grauberg/Fort Karugo-Narugo/East Ronfaure/North Gustaberg/West Sarutabaruta].
        WE_HAVE_RECEIVED_UNCONFIRMED_REPORTS_THAT_A_MEDIUM                    = 13059,  -- We have received unconfirmed reports that a medium-sized Beastman force is stationed in [Xarcabard/Beaucedine Glacier/The Eldieme Necropolis/Crawlers' Nest/Garlaige Citadel/Batallia Downs/the Rolanberry Fields/Sauromugue Champaign/Jugner Forest/Pashhow Marshlands/the Meriphataud Mountains/Vunkerl Inlet/Grauberg/Fort Karugo-Narugo/East Ronfaure/North Gustaberg/West Sarutabaruta].
        WE_HAVE_RECEIVED_UNCONFIRMED_REPORTS_THAT_A_SMALL                     = 13060,  -- We have received unconfirmed reports that a small-sized Dark Kindred force is stationed in [Xarcabard/Beaucedine Glacier/The Eldieme Necropolis/Crawlers' Nest/Garlaige Citadel/Batallia Downs/the Rolanberry Fields/Sauromugue Champaign/Jugner Forest/Pashhow Marshlands/the Meriphataud Mountains/Vunkerl Inlet/Grauberg/Fort Karugo-Narugo/East Ronfaure/North Gustaberg/West Sarutabaruta].
        WE_HAVE_RECEIVED_UNCONFIRMED_REPORTS_THAT_A_BEASTMAN                  = 13061,  -- We have received unconfirmed reports that a Beastman supply convoy has been spotted in [Xarcabard/Beaucedine Glacier/The Eldieme Necropolis/Crawlers' Nest/Garlaige Citadel/Batallia Downs/the Rolanberry Fields/Sauromugue Champaign/Jugner Forest/Pashhow Marshlands/the Meriphataud Mountains/Vunkerl Inlet/Grauberg/Fort Karugo-Narugo/East Ronfaure/North Gustaberg/West Sarutabaruta].
        THAT_IS_ALL_THE_INTEL_WORTH_MENTIONING_THAT                           = 13062,  -- That is all the intel worth mentioning that we have at this time. If you have anything to contribute to our stratagems, now would be the time.
        TO_WHICH_AREA_DO_YOU_THINK_IT_WISEST                                  = 13063,  -- To which area do you think it wisest to dispatch a supply convoy?
        WHERE_WOULD_YOU_SEND_THE_SUPPLY_CONVOY_XARCABARD                      = 13064,  -- Where would you send the supply convoy? Xarcabard. Beaucedine Glacier. The Eldieme Necropolis. Crawlers' Nest. Garlaige Citadel. Batallia Downs. Rolanberry Fields. Sauromugue Champaign. Jugner Forest. Pashhow Marshlands. Meriphataud Mountains. Vunkerl Inlet. Grauberg. Fort Karugo-Narugo. East Ronfaure. North Gustaberg. West Sarutabaruta.
        I_SEE_AND_HOW_MUCH_CARGO_WOULD_YOU                                    = 13065,  -- I see. And how much cargo would you think it prudent for them to take?
        IT_GOES_WITHOUT_SAYING_THAT_THE_MORE_SUPPLIES                         = 13066,  -- It goes without saying that the more supplies there are, the happier the troops on location will be.
        WHAT_AMOUNT_DO_YOU_RECOMMEND_A_LARGE_AMOUNT                           = 13067,  -- What amount do you recommend? A large amount. A moderate amount. A small amount.
        VERY_WELL_AND_DO_YOU_HAVE_ANY_THOUGHTS                                = 13068,  -- Very well. And do you have any thoughts on which route it would be best for the convoy to take?
        WHICH_ROUTE_DO_YOU_ENDORSE_THE_QUICKEST_SHORTEST                      = 13069,  -- Which route do you endorse? The quickest, shortest route possible. The normal route used in peacetime. The safest detouring route.
        BASED_ON_THAT_ROUTE_WE_MUST_CONSIDER_NEXT                             = 13070,  -- Based on that route, we must consider next the convoy's escort. How large a force do you believe most appropriate?
        WHAT_SIZE_ESCORT_DO_YOU_SUGGEST_A_MEDIUM                              = 13071,  -- What size escort do you suggest? A medium-sized force. A small-sized force. A minimum-sized force.
        I_HAVE_ONE_LAST_INQUIRY_SHOULD_THE_CONVOY                             = 13072,  -- I have one last inquiry. Should the convoy encounter an enemy contingent, Goddess forbid, what course of action should they take?
        FIGHT_OR_FLIGHT_ENGAGE_IN_OPEN_BATTLE_AVOID                           = 13073,  -- Fight or flight? Engage in open battle. Avoid conflict at all cost.
        ALRIGHT_I_BELIEVE_THAT_COVERS_EVERYTHING_DO_YOU                       = 13074,  -- Alright, I believe that covers everything. Do you have any amendments you wish to make before issuing these suggestions?
        EDIT_YOUR_SUBMISSION_NO_IT_S_SOLID_ON                                 = 13075,  -- Edit your submission? No, it's solid. On second thought, yes.
        EXCELLENT_THEN_I_SHALL_DO_MY_UTMOST_TO                                = 13076,  -- Excellent. Then I shall do my utmost to see to it your tactics are implemented in tomorrow's operations.
        AS_THE_MASTERMIND_BEHIND_THE_ARMY_S_STRATEGY                          = 13077,  -- As the mastermind behind the army's strategy for this operation, it is customary for you to travel to the stronghold in question. From there you will be able to observe the execution of your plans.
