        I_HAVE_BEEN_CONTEMPLATING_THIS_FOR_SOME_TIME                          = 13356,  -- I have been contemplating this for some time now. The Young Griffons will be disbanded, as was Excenmille's parting wish.
        WH_WHAT_3                                                             = 13357,  -- Wh-what!?
