        SCENE_EDITING_SHORTCUT_0_1_4_5_6                                      = 13402,  -- Scene Editing Shortcut. 0 1 4 5 6 7 8 9 10
        WELL_YOU_RE_CERTAINLY_LOOKING_QUITE_HAPLESS_ADVENTURER                = 13403,  -- Well, you're certainly looking quite hapless, adventurer. Have you not your wits about you?
        WHAT_S_ALL_THE_COMMOTION_YOU_ASK_WELL                                 = 13404,  -- What's all the commotion, you ask? Well, everyone is on their way to see Troupe Mayakov's performance, of course. My comrades have been scrambling about relentlessly for some time now trying to procure tickets.
        SURELY_YOU_ARE_FAMILIAR_WITH_TROUPE_MAYAKOV_YES                       = 13405,  -- Surely you are familiar with Troupe Mayakov, yes?
        ARE_YOU_FAMILIAR_WITH_TROUPE_MAYAKOV_NO_NOT                           = 13406,  -- Are you familiar with Troupe Mayakov? No, not at all familiar. Yes, exceedingly familiar.
        WHAT_I_CANNOT_EVEN_BEGIN_TO_IMAGINE_THE                               = 13407,  -- What!? I cannot even begin to imagine the enormity of the rock under which you must have been hiding. Why, they are one of the most popular dancing troupes in Vana'diel right now, rivaled perhaps only by Troupe Brilioth.
        THOUGH_FROM_A_STYLISTIC_AND_TECHNICAL_POINT_OF                        = 13408,  -- Though from a stylistic and technical point of view, I am of the personal opinion that Troupe Mayakov is considerably more advanced.
        OF_COURSE_IT_CERTAINLY_DOESN_T_HURT_THAT                              = 13409,  -- Of course, it certainly doesn't hurt that they have amassed some of the most adorable dancers I've ever seen!
        AS_WELL_YOU_SHOULD_THEY_VE_COME_TO                                    = 13410,  -- As well you should! They've come to gain quite the reputation amongst the people recently for their lineup of beauties. Only the finest are selected, they say.
        IN_FACT_A_SHOW_IS_ABOUT_TO_START                                      = 13411,  -- In fact, a show is about to start over at the old tavern in Lion Square. The troupe leader has decided to grace San d'Oria with a performance by popular demand.
        SUCH_A_CHANCE_TO_SEE_PERFORMERS_OF_THAT                               = 13412,  -- Such a chance to see performers of that caliber up close doesn't present itself very often. Everyone sure is up in a frenzy over it, all right.
        WELL_IF_YOU_HAVE_TIME_YOURSELF_I_WOULD                                = 13413,  -- Well, if you have time yourself, I would highly recommend you pay a visit. Although I offer no guarantee that you'll be able to get your hands on a ticket.
        WHAT_I_WOULDN_T_GIVE_TO_NOT_BE                                        = 13414,  -- What I wouldn't give to not be on guard duty... <Sigh>...
        MR_MAYAKOV_LET_ME_FIRST_OF_ALL_THANK                                  = 13415,  -- Mr. Mayakov, let me first of all thank you for taking the time to speak with us here today. We know that you are a busy man.
        NOW_PLEASE_SIR_IF_YOU_WOULD_SHARE_WITH                                = 13416,  -- Now please, sir, if you would, share with us what you consider to be the highlight of this, your latest show.
        IT_WOULD_BE_MY_PLEATHURE_ATH_I_M                                      = 13417,  -- It would be my pleathure. Ath I'm thure you all know by now, my Troupe Mayakov only incorporateth the motht beautiful and dathling of elementth into ith danth.
        HOWEVER_IT_HATH_COME_TO_MY_ATTENTION_ATH                              = 13418,  -- However, it hath come to my attention ath of late, that we have reached the abtholute pinnacle of vithible aeththetic beauty.
        WELL_ERRR_THAT_S                                                      = 13419,  -- Well, errr... That's...
        AND_THO_ONE_REATHON_I_HAVE_COME_HERE                                  = 13420,  -- And tho one reathon I have come here today ith to make it known that thome time ago I made it our troupe philothophy to theek out new horithonth and new challengeth. To be true vanguardth of our art.
        AND_GUIDED_BY_THAT_PHILOTHOPHY_I_HAVE_DITHCOVERED                     = 13421,  -- And guided by that philothophy, I have dithcovered a new theme for our danthe. A new realm to throw ourthelveth into. A new moduth operandi by which to move and bring delight to our audienth. "Dreamth"!
        THROUGH_OUR_DANTHE_AND_OUR_ART_WE_HOPE                                = 13422,  -- Through our danthe and our art, we hope to bring dreamth to everyone in their troubled timeth.
