        THE_MAJETHTIC_DRAWING_OF_THE_CURTAIN_THE_DATHLING                     = 13424,  -- The majethtic drawing of the curtain! The dathling thine of the thpotlight! And then! The unparalleled beauty and grathe of my danthing angelth!
        THE_FLYING_OF_THWEAT_OFF_OF_PATHION_DRIVEN                            = 13425,  -- The flying of thweat off of pathion-driven browth! The hypnotic clicking of heelth on the hard, polithed, wooden thtage! I promithe to thend our audienthe home with an evening of rapture they will not thoon forget!
