        BUT_MR_MAYAKOV_WHAT_IS_YOUR_RESPONSE_THEN                             = 13427,  -- But, Mr. Mayakov, what is your response, then, to pundits who claim that the current state of affairs is not particularly conducive to the continuation of extravagant arts such as dance?
        UTTER_NONTHENTH                                                       = 13428,  -- Utter nonthenth!
