        I_APPRETHIATE_YOUR_ENTHUTHIATHM_BUT_I_M_AFRAID                        = 13437,  -- I apprethiate your enthuthiathm, but I'm afraid we are thtill undergoing pre-thow preparathionth. I'll have to athk you to leave for the time being, but be thure to come back later with your ticket.
