        OOOH_THIR_RAGELITHE_OF_THE_KNIGHTH_OF_THE                             = 13470,  -- Oooh! Thir Ragelithe of the Knighth of the Ironcretht Hawk. It ith a motht profound honor for Troupe Mayakov to be blethed by your cuthtom!
        WE_HAVE_BEEN_EAGERLY_AWAITING_YOUR_ARRIVAL_THIR                       = 13471,  -- We have been eagerly awaiting your arrival, thir! The finetht theat in the houthe hath been prepared for your viewing pleathure and comfort!
        I_AM_MOST_PLEASED_TO_HEAR_THAT_WHAT                                   = 13472,  -- I am most pleased to hear that. What's this? Is there some trouble?
        NO_THIR_NOT_AT_ALL_THIMPLY_ANOTHER_FAN                                = 13473,  -- No, thir, not at all. Thimply another fan trying to gain entry with a fake ticket. You needn't worry yourthelf. We have matterth well under control.
        I_EVEN_HAVE_HALF_A_MIND_TO_ORDER                                      = 13474,  -- I even have half a mind to order them all rounded up and thrown into Ronfaure for their detheit!
        I_M_AFRAID_I_CAN_T_STAND_IDLY                                         = 13475,  -- I'm afraid I can't stand idly by and let you treat my friend in such a manner.
