        THAT_S_CORRECT_ISN_T_THAT_RIGHT_SO                                    = 13477,  -- That's correct. Isn't that right? So please, some leniency, I beg of you.
        MY_PROFUTHE_APOLOGIETH_THIR_RAGELITHE_I_INTENDED_NO                   = 13478,  -- My profuthe apologieth, Thir Ragelithe! I intended no dithrethpect.
        INDEED_A_FRIEND_OF_OUR_GREAT_AND_NOBLE                                = 13479,  -- Indeed, a friend of our great and noble guetht, Thir Ragelithe, thall be more than welcome by Troupe Mayakov.
        FORGIVE_MY_IMPERTINENTHE_TROUPE_MAYAKOV_ITH_HONORED_BY                = 13480,  -- Forgive my impertinenthe. Troupe Mayakov ith honored by your patronage.
        THE_PERFORMANTHE_WILL_BEGIN_MOMENTARILY_PLEATHE_HURRY_TO              = 13481,  -- The performanthe will begin momentarily. Pleathe hurry to your theatth!
        WELL_THAT_WAS_A_CLOSE_CALL_WOULDN_T                                   = 13482,  -- Well, that was a close call, wouldn't you say? Artists! Haha, the troupe leader is by no means a bad fellow. But he certainly can be a stubborn and selfish one.
        YOU_CAUGHT_MY_EYE_BY_THE_DOOR_THERE                                   = 13483,  -- You caught my eye by the door, there, adventurer. You have an air of regality about you. You are a knight of the Kingdom, yes?
        AHHH_SERVING_UNDER_GRAND_KNIGHT_RONGELOUTS_IN_THE                     = 13484,  -- Ahhh, serving under Grand Knight Rongelouts in the Knights of the Iron Ram, are you?
        I_HAD_HEARD_THAT_A_RECENT_ADDITION_TO                                 = 13485,  -- I had heard that a recent addition to his ranks was turning out to be an exemplary recruit. No doubt it was you this rumor was in reference to.
        OF_THE_REPUBLIC_YOU_SAY_A_BASTOKER_ARE                                = 13486,  -- Of the Republic, you say? A Bastoker, are you? In the Seventh Legionnaires? That sounds vaguely familiar...
        AH_YES_OF_COURSE_LED_BY_PRAEFECTUS_ZAZARG                             = 13487,  -- Ah, yes, of course! Led by Praefectus Zazarg, if I recall correctly. A position to be proud of.
        WINDURST_YOU_DON_T_SAY_AND_ONE_OF                                     = 13488,  -- Windurst!? You don't say! And one of the Cobra Mercenaries, no less? That explains the hardened look in your eyes. No doubt you have plenty a story to tell.
        NEARLY_EVERYONE_BY_NOW_KNOWS_OF_THE_CAPABLE                           = 13489,  -- Nearly everyone by now knows of the capable command of your Romaa Mihgo. The tales of her deeds reach us even here in San d'Oria.
        I_NEEDN_T_TELL_YOU_THEN_OF_THE                                        = 13490,  -- I needn't tell you, then, of the horrors of this great war. The ranks of the Beastman Confederate stretch in all directions with no end in sight. We in the service of the Allied Forces rarely have a free moment to enjoy the very freedoms we fight for.
        WHICH_IS_WHY_IT_IS_SO_ESSENTIAL_THAT                                  = 13491,  -- Which is why it is so essential that we make the most of our time away from duty. To forget the troubles and worries that this war has thrust upon us, and to enjoy what little time we have with our friends and loved ones.
        THAT_IS_WHY_I_SPOKE_UP_ON_YOUR                                        = 13492,  -- That is why I spoke up on your behalf at the door.
        HM_WHO_AM_I_OH_WELL_THAT_S                                            = 13493,  -- Hm? Who am I? Oh, well, that's neither here nor there. Consider me no more than a fellow soldier.
        BUT_LET_US_SPEAK_NOW_OF_WHAT_BRINGS                                   = 13494,  -- But let us speak now of what brings us here. The critics are touting Troupe Mayakov's performance as the show to see! And I can attest firsthand to the quality of the dancers. Come, come. Let us enjoy the evening.
