        SHE_ONLY_JUST_RECENTLY_JOINED_THE_TROUPE_BUT                          = 13512,  -- She only just recently joined the troupe. But apparently she was able to pass their stringent screening on the first go. No easy feat, that. Troupe Mayakov is notoriously strict in their recruiting practices.
