        NO_DOUBT_THAT_AURA_OF_MYSTERY_HAS_HELPED                              = 13515,  -- No doubt that aura of mystery has helped to propel her to such stardom so quickly. If there's one thing people love, it's the effect of the exotic. We love the unknown.
        AND_SO_THE_FLUTTERING_OF_THE_BUTTERFLY_S                              = 13516,  -- And so the fluttering of the butterfly's flight draws to a close. Did you find yourself traipsing the night winds with her, guided by the light of the moon?
