        THE_LEADER_OF_THE_TEMPLE_KNIGHTS_IS_CURILLA                           = 14090,  -- The leader of the Temple Knights is... Curilla V Mecru. Yrvaulair S Cousseraux. Febrenard C Brunnaut.
        THE_LEADER_OF_THE_ROYAL_GUARDS_IS_ALTEDOUR                            = 14091,  -- The leader of the Royal Guards is... Altedour I Tavnazia. Valaineral R Davilles. Ragelise B Baloumat.
