        NEXT_PHANTOM_THIS_APPARITION_WILL_ENVELOP_ITS_FOES                    = 14169,  -- Next: Phantom! This apparition will envelop its foes in a shroud of deadly curses. Beware these spectral assassins of the Underworld!
        AND_LAST_BUT_NOT_LEAST_SCORPION_THE_RAZOR                             = 14170,  -- And last but not least: Scorpion! The razor-sharp stinger of this creature can rip right through opponents. Scorpions are the shock troopers of arthropod society!
        THE_ROCK_S_UNCOMPROMISING_HARDNESS_WILL_SHATTER_THE                   = 14171,  -- The rock's uncompromising hardness will shatter the scorpion's stinger...
        BUT_BE_INEFFECTIVE_AGAINST_THE_INSIDIOUS_CURSES_OF                    = 14172,  -- ...But be ineffective against the insidious curses of the phantom.
        THE_PHANTOM_S_DIAPHANOUS_FORM_WILL_CLOAK_THE                          = 14173,  -- The phantom's diaphanous form will cloak the rock in ethereal curses...
        BUT_BE_EASILY_RIPPED_TO_PIECES_BY_THE                                 = 14174,  -- ...But be easily ripped to pieces by the scorpion's stinger.
        THE_SCORPION_S_MENACING_STINGER_WILL_TEAR_THE                         = 14175,  -- The scorpion's menacing stinger will tear the phantom to shreds...
        BUT_BREAK_AGAINST_THE_UNBENDING_SURFACE_OF_THE                        = 14176,  -- ...But break against the unbending surface of the rock.
        THROUGH_RPS_TRAINING_SOLDIERS_ARE_INSTILLED_WITH_THE                  = 14177,  -- Through RPS training, soldiers are instilled with the observation skills necessary to identify and exploit an enemy's weakness. Naturally, luck too has a role to play in the outcome, as it does on the battlefield. Were you able to digest all that, maggot?
        NOW_THEN_LET_US_BEGIN_THE_FIRST_TO                                    = 14178,  -- Now then. Let us begin. The first to win three rounds shall be declared the victor.
