        YOUR_TROUPE_S_IS_A_RECOGNIZED_AND_RESPECTED                           = 14343,  -- Your troupe's is a recognized and respected name across the realm. Further, I know full well that your people can hold their own in battle should the need arise, heaven forfend. I would be loath to entrust a role of such import to any other.
